-- Cameroon Average Cocoa Farmgate Price Drops 0.2% in Wk to May 7
-- B y   P i u s   L u k o n g
-- 2013-05-08T14:12:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-08/cameroon-average-cocoa-farmgate-price-drops-0-2-in-wk-to-may-7.html
Cameroon’s average national farmgate
cocoa price fell 0.2% to 998 CFA francs/kg in wk to May 7 from
1,000 francs wk earlier, according to Bloomberg calculations
from data provided by Cameroon National Association of Cocoa and
Coffee Producers.  Following is a table of regional farmgate rates, with
prices/kg in CFA francs.  Southwest
-Kumba    1010
-Mamfe    1000
South      980
Center    1000
Littoral  1000
Average    998  To contact the reporter on this story:
